songs.title: That’s My Girl (Jimmie Club Remix)
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
You've been, you've been

[Verse 1: Ally]
Who's been working so damn hard?
You got that head on overload?
Got yourself this flawless body
Aching now from head to toe

[Refrain: Normani & Ally]
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing
All my ladies 'round the world
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing

[Pre-Chorus: Lauren]
You've been down before
You've been hurt before
You got up before
You'll be good to go, good to go

[Chorus: Normani]
Destiny said it, you got to get up and get it
Get mad independent and don't you ever forget it
Got some dirt on your shoulder, then let me brush it off for ya
If you're feeling me, put your five high

[Post-Chorus: Camila]
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl

[Breakdown: Camila & Ally & Lauren]
High, high, hi-hi-high
High, high, hi-hi-high
That's my girl
High, high, hi-hi-high
High, high, hi-hi-high
(That's my girl)
High, high, hi-hi-high
High, high, hi-hi-high
(That's my girl)
What ya wait, what ya wait, whatya waiting for?
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl

[Verse 2: Dinah]
Nod if you been played by every boo
Just tryna show you off
Thought he was the best you ever had
Until he

[Refrain: Normani & Ally]
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing
Bet you bet you know your worth
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing

[Pre-Chorus: Lauren]
You've been down before
You've been hurt before
You got up before
You'll be good to go, good to go

[Chorus: Normani]
Destiny said it, you got to get up and get it
Get mad independent and don't you ever forget it
Got some dirt on your shoulder, then let me brush it off for ya
If you're feeling me, put your five high

[Post-Chorus: Camila]
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl
That's my girl

[Breakdown: Camila & Ally & Lauren]
High, high, hi-hi-high
High, high, hi-hi-high
That's my girl
High, high, hi-hi-high
High, high, hi-hi-high
That's my girl

[Bridge: Normani & Ally]
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing, ain't nothing
Put your heart and your soul in it
High, high, hi-hi-high
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing, ain't nothing
(Now put your heart and your soul in it)
High, high, hi-hi-high
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing, ain't nothing
Put your heart and your soul in it
High, high, hi-hi-high
Ain't nothing, ain't nothing, ain't nothing
(Now put your heart and your soul in it)
High, high, hi-hi-high
